<br>
Baldurs Gate 2:  Throne of Bhaal - This is the Expansion,  Comes out Summer 2001.<br>
<br>
Neverwinter nights - I am not sure when this is suppose to come out.  I think Spring 2001.<br>
<br>
Pools of Radiance - Another 3rd Ed AD&amp;D game.  This one looks very cool,  made by SSI.  Not sure on release date,  sometime either spring or summer this year.<br>
<br>
The Sims: House party:  Just went Gold.  Expansion, sounds pretty cool,  I will break out the Sims for this.<br>
<br>
IceWind Dale: Heart of Winter - Expansion pack, this adds More Lvls,  More Spells,  And new places to hunt.  Supposedly it is out now.<br>
<br>
Tribes 2 - Can anyone say Delay?  This has been being pushed back since Decemeber.<br>
<br>
The Summoner - RPG game that looks cool.  It is suppose to be out this month.<br>
<br>
Deus Ex 2 - Suppose to be next month.<br>
<br>
Team Fortress 2 - Next Month,  this is suppsoe to be a stand alone game instead of a MOD.  Using a enhanced Half Life Engine.<br>
<br>
Unreal 2 - Apirl,  we wills ee if this gets out on time.....not sure if I will buy it anyways,  iw as rather disappointed with unreal.<br>
<br>
Thief III - May 2001.  I Love this series of games.<br>
<br>
<br>
There is alot of RPG's coming out in the next year,  and many Online Games.  Soverign, Ultima Worlds Online: Origin, Horizon,  Anarchy Online, Shadowbane, and many others.  I didnt list any of these because I havent got the full list of them,  alot are being done by Development houses,  but dont have any money behind them.  It hink Horizon and Origin look very good.  But unfortunately Horizon already stopped development once because of no money,  then they got some money from somewhere,  but they already said that it isnt enough to finish the game,  so we will have to see where that one goes.<br>
<br>
I will update this list soon.  Tell me if theres any games you guys are excited about.<br>
<br>
Shular <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ushular.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shular</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Retired One</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/01 12:01:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/fashesofragefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=250.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Check this one out</span><hr size=1> I know I am oin to uy this one:<br>
